---
import Layout from "../layouts/BlogPost.astro";
---

<Layout
	title="About Me"
	description="Learn more about Ivan Trajanovski, a mobile developer based in Austria"
	pubDate={new Date("January 20 2025")}
	heroImage="/blog-placeholder-about.jpg"
>
	<p>Hello! I'm Ivan Trajanovski, a mobile developer based in Autria.</p>

	<h2>Professional Journey</h2>
	<p>
		I started my development career in web development, before transitioning into 
		Data Science and ML. But, I had a passion for mobile development, and soon after
		switched to a Flutter position.
	</p>

	<h2>Skills</h2>
	<div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-8">
		<div>
			<h3>Languages</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>JavaScript</li>
				<li>Dart</li>
				<li>Swift</li>
				<li>Java</li>
				<li>Python</li>
				<li>Perl</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<div>
			<h3>Frameworks</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>Flutter</li>
				<li>Astro</li>
				<li>SwiftUI</li>
				<li>NextJS</li>
				<li>Node</li>
				<li>React</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<div>
			<h3>Databases</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>PostgreSQL</li>
				<li>Firebase</li>
				<li>Supabase</li>
				<li>MongoDB</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<div>
			<h3>Tools</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>Docker</li>
				<li>Kubernetes</li>
				<li>Git</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>

	<h2>Beyond Coding</h2>
	<p>
		When I'm not coding, I enjoy writing, reading fantasy books(I'm a big fan of
		Brandon Sanderson), skiing, watching football.
	</p>

	<h2>Let's Connect</h2>
	<p>
		I'm always interested in connecting with other people. 
		Whether you want to discuss mobile development, potential
		projects, or just want to say hi, feel free to reach out!
	</p>
</Layout>
